alias ddevUnitTest="ddev exec typo3DatabaseDriver='mysqli' typo3DatabaseHost='db' typo3DatabasePort=3306 typo3DatabaseUsername='root' typo3DatabasePassword='root' typo3DatabaseName='func' php vendor/bin/phpunit"
alias "git co"="git checkout"
alias gst="git status"
alias gc="git commit"
alias gcm="git commit -m"
alias gp="git push"
alias gw="git switch"
alias cloud="ssh jdelesky@cloud.local"
alias n="nvim"
alias lg="lazygit"
alias t=tmux
alias dtf="ddev typo3 cache:flush & echo 'flushing typo3 cache'"
#alias gsm="git switch $(awk -F "/" "{print \$NF}" .git/refs/remotes/origin/HEAD)"
#alias gmm="git merge --no-ff $(awk -F "/" "{print \$NF}" .git/refs/remotes/origin/HEAD)"

# Switch to the default branch from origin
gsm() {
  if git rev-parse --is-inside-work-tree &>/dev/null && \
     git remote show origin &>/dev/null; then
    branch=$(git symbolic-ref --short refs/remotes/origin/HEAD 2>/dev/null | awk -F/ '{print $NF}')
    if [[ -n "$branch" ]]; then
      git switch "$branch"
    else
      echo "Could not detect default remote branch."
    fi
  else
    echo "Not in a Git repository or 'origin' remote not found."
  fi
}

# Merge with the default branch from origin
gmm() {
  if git rev-parse --is-inside-work-tree &>/dev/null && \
     git remote show origin &>/dev/null; then
    branch=$(git symbolic-ref --short refs/remotes/origin/HEAD 2>/dev/null | awk -F/ '{print $NF}')
    if [[ -n "$branch" ]]; then
      git merge --no-ff "$branch"
    else
      echo "Could not detect default remote branch."
    fi
  else
    echo "Not in a Git repository or 'origin' remote not found."
  fi
}

cflush() {
  echo "🔍 Checking DDEV project status..."

  # Check if inside a DDEV project
  if ! ddev describe &>/dev/null; then
    echo "❌ Not inside a DDEV project (no .ddev directory or DDEV not initialized)."
    return 1
  fi

  echo "✅ DDEV project detected."

  # Detect available TYPO3 console command (TYPO3 v12+ uses 'typo3', older uses 'typo3cms')
  if ddev exec test -x ./vendor/bin/typo3 &>/dev/null; then
    TYPO3_CMD="./vendor/bin/typo3"
  elif ddev exec test -x ./vendor/bin/typo3cms &>/dev/null; then
    TYPO3_CMD="./vendor/bin/typo3cms"
  else
    echo "❌ No TYPO3 console found (neither typo3 nor typo3cms)."
    return 1
  fi

  echo "🔄 Flushing TYPO3 cache using: $TYPO3_CMD cache:flush"

  # Execute the cache flush
  if ddev exec $TYPO3_CMD cache:flush; then
    echo "✅ TYPO3 cache successfully flushed."
  else
    echo "❌ Failed to flush TYPO3 cache."
    return 1
  fi
}
